dct_title_s: Riparian map of properties along the Hudson River, Englewood, Palisade and Harrington Townships, New Jersey
dct_description_sm: Riparian map featuring the high water lines pertaining to various individually owned and business properties along the Hudson River in Englewood, Palisade and Harrington Townships, New Jersey.
Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection
Latest date found on map is 1881; date is inferred
